                               <h1 class="text-align-center" id="yui_3_17_2_63_1461022048731_456"><strong>LnB</strong>
                               </h1>
                               <h1 class="text-align-center">
                                  World's Most Innovative Lender
                               </h1>
                               <p class="text-align-center" id="yui_3_17_2_63_1461022048731_1404">
                                  Many people need money for a variety of reasons such as rent, tuition, allowance, home improvement but have hard time finding a lender. Since the last financial crisis in 2008, the biggest lenders,&nbsp;the banks, have been hesitant to lend money and perform deep scrutiny into the borrower. So the alternative lenders came into spotlight but even those have problems.&nbsp;For example, payday lenders are extremely expensive and the borrowing amount is limited and need to pay back quickly.&nbsp;P2P lenders are not for everyone as it requires good credit and takes a long time for the application to be approved. It is awkward to ask family and friends for money.&nbsp;Credit card companies allow for people to take cash advances but they are very expensive and allow only small amount of money to be borrowed. So LnB came out with a solution with new type of borrowing which will offer either CHEAPER rate or both compared to any other lenders.
                               </p>
